{"tid":1285980,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"TG谷 歡迎90後入黎無腦傾計","createTime":"2019-07-04T17:47:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T04:09:31.000Z","uid":81999,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"922bab5d0c8f8ba90bd3f06645b96e0930c7d248","tid":1285980,"uid":81999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:47:29.000Z","msg":"最近因為反送中條例，無收到人！<br />\n家陣重新收人啦～快啲黎一齊吹水啦<br />\n<br />\nTG我地真係無腦谷 收人入黎吹水扮工啦<br />\n沉悶既生活無限loop!? 無腦吹水就岩哂你啦~ 歡迎鐘意吹水扮工既你.<br />\n係咪覺得返工、返學好無聊。日日起身都好似ON99咁，無乜目標，就係因為你地未加入我地呢個90後吹水扮工谷啦！！<br />\n我地呢度大量吹水9UP，可以識下朋友之如又可以HEA到時間，手機食雞打機，行山睇戲食飯北上飲油都會定期搞下.<br />\n快D入黎一齊吹水啦！<br />\n只要混得熟我地，貴谷絕對高質好玩又好笑，熟左之後歡迎鬥mean. 但請不要人生攻擊, 謝謝<br />\n歡迎90後加入我地，只要有心吹水，我們都歡迎。<br />\n在此溫馨提示，本谷七天平均MSG 維持~15000，有心上水就請填以下表格。<br />\n謝絕狗公娘娘, 如有投訴會處理.<br />\nAdmin會盡快處理收人.<br />\n<br />\n想入谷就填左以下張表格先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/u/2/d/133DcrocCVTyhHCEd-blwSmlH9H3huhyKJSMG5pGDsAk/edit?usp=sharing_eip&amp;ts=5ce4c217\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fu%2F2%2Fd%2F133DcrocCVTyhHCEd-blwSmlH9H3huhyKJSMG5pGDsAk%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing_eip%26ts%3D5ce4c217&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRUcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=8a6e9a26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/u/2/d/133DcrocCVTyhHCEd-blwSmlH9H3huhyKJSMG5pGDsAk/edit?usp=sharing_eip&amp;ts=5ce4c217</a>"},{"pid":"8d318ac41f35f941df29410a983b30918b66cc75","tid":1285980,"uid":81999,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:27:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8ce2155310dc0ab39c1dd4a054ab3d912611b9b","tid":1285980,"uid":81999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201